## Running the Pipeline

### Prerequisites

- Python 3.12+
- Java 17 (required by Spark)
- UV package manager

```bash
# Install dependencies
uv sync

# Generate Parquet fixtures (first time)
make generate-fixtures
```

### Local Execution

```bash
# Run directly
python -m etl_agent.spark.generated.pipeline_{{ pipeline_name | lower }}

# Override paths
python -m etl_agent.spark.generated.pipeline_{{ pipeline_name | lower }} \
  --source s3://my-bucket/raw/ \
  --target s3://my-bucket/processed/

# Via the CLI
etl-agent run --story config/story_examples/{{ story_id }}.yaml
```

### Via Docker Compose

```bash
make up          # Start all services
make demo        # Run the full agent demo (creates PR automatically)
make logs        # Stream app logs
```

